      <title>高盛不再预期美国5月降息</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/goldman-sachs-no-longer-expects-us-interest-rate-cut-may-2024-02-23/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛分析师不再预期美国 5 月份降息，并预计今年将有四次降息 25 个基点，因为政策制定者的言论表明他们并不着急。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/goldman-sachs-no-longer-expects-us-interest-rate-cut-may-2024-02-23/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 23 Feb 2024 04:02:13 GMT</pubDate>
